comments: Braun (DEN) brings his forearm toward Agbaji's (UTA) body, and marginal contact occurs during his driving shot attempt.
Fontecchio (UTA) legally contests Cancar's (DEN) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.
Watson (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball as he contests Dunn's (UTA) driving shot attempt.
Watson (DEN) goes to, not through, Fontecchio's (UTA) space, and marginal contact occurs prior to his gather.
Fontecchio (UTA) jumps from point A to point B and makes contact with Watson (DEN), which dislodges him during his pass.
Watson (DEN) briefly brings his arm toward Dunn's (UTA) body, and marginal contact occurs during Dunn's drive.
Azubuike (UTA) establishes himself in Braun's (DEN) path and absorbs the incidental contact to his upper body as the off-ball screen is set.
Watson (DEN) goes to, not through, Dunn (UTA) and marginal contact occurs as they come together at the end of the drive.
Cancar (DEN) extends both hands forward and initiates contact with Toscano-Anderson (UTA) to commit a take foul.
Braun (DEN) makes clean contact with the ball and dislodges it away from Agbaji (UTA) prior to incidental contact occurring.
Dunn (UTA) initiates contact with Braun (DEN) that affects his SQBR as he attempts to make the pass.
Dunn (UTA) releases the pass before returning to the floor.
Smith (DEN) comes across Agbaji's (UTA) arm, which affects his SQBR.
The game is stopped due to a game clock malfunction. After communicating with the Replay Center, the game clock is reset to 11.4.
Dunn (UTA) brings both hands toward Smith (DEN) and marginal contact occurs as Smith  retrieves the inbound pass.
Samanic (UTA) brushes Cancar's (DEN) arm and marginal contact occurs as Cancar is able to retrieve the pass.

Smith (DEN) collides with his teammate when both players are in pursuit of the rebound, and an inadvertent whistle is blown. After the inadvertent whistle, the clock is reset to 1.5, and due to neither team maintaining control or imminent control of the ball, the play results in a jump ball.
